OL,3,CAssisted dying could be legal on Isle
OL,4,Cof Man by 2027 after delay rejected
OL,6,FAssisting dying could become an option
OL,7,Fon the Isle of Man as soon as 2027
OL,8,Fafter a move to delay it was narrowly
OL,9,Fdefeated.
OL,11,FMembers of the House of Keys (MHK)
OL,12,Fvoted 12 to 11 to reject a proposal of
OL,13,Fa referendum to be held, which would
OL,14,Fhave delayed any legislation coming
OL,15,Finto effect.
OL,17,FIt means the bill, which is currently
OL,18,Fbeing scrutinised by MHKs, is expected
OL,19,Fto receive a Third Reading in the
OL,20,FHouse of Keys in the coming months.
