OL,3,CAssisted dying could be legal on Isle
OL,4,Cof Man by 2027 after delay rejected
OL,6,FDebates have so far decided that those
OL,7,Fwho have been given a prognosis of 12
OL,8,Fmonths left to live would be able to
OL,9,Fuse the proposed law, where they would
OL,10,Fhave to take life-ending medications
OL,11,Fthemselves rather than being
OL,12,Fadministered by a doctor.
OL,14,FThe bill puts the Isle of Man on the
OL,15,Fpath to become the first part of the
OL,16,FBritish Isles to legalise assisted
OL,17,Fdying.
