OL,3,CAssisted dying could be legal on Isle
OL,4,Cof Man by 2027 after delay rejected
OL,6,FDr Alex Allinson introduced the
OL,7,FPrivate Member's Bill in 2022 in his
OL,8,Fcapacity as a MHK for the Ramsey area
OL,9,Fon the Island.
OL,11,FThe GP, who is also the Isle of Man
OL,12,Fgovernment's Treasury Minister, said
OL,13,Fhe is confident the Island's
OL,14,Fparliament has the time to "craft the
OL,15,Fright bill".
OL,17,FAnti-assisted dying campaigner Peter
OL,18,FMurcott has said the assisted dying
OL,19,Fbill has "many legal flaws", and is
OL,20,F"against the will of God".
