OL,3,CAssisted dying could be legal on Isle
OL,4,Cof Man by 2027 after delay rejected
OL,6,FThe former law lecturer describes the
OL,7,Fbill as 'assisted suicide', claiming
OL,8,Fthat there are many on the island who
OL,9,Fare against the proposed change.
OL,11,FSpeaking outside Tynwald, he said: "On
OL,12,FMay 17 2023, government adopted a
OL,13,Fsuicide prevention strategy. Now this
OL,14,Fbecomes a suicide provision strategy,
OL,15,Fbecause the bill is about assisted
OL,16,Fsuicide, about amending the existing
OL,17,Flaw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
