OL,3,CAssisted dying could be legal on Isle
OL,4,Cof Man by 2027 after delay rejected
OL,6,F"I cannot understand how you can spend
OL,7,Fpublic money on providing something
OL,8,Fthat you're going to prevent because
OL,9,Fthe prevention strategy takes public
OL,10,Fmoney, and this bill will take public
OL,11,Fmoney - trying to do two contradictory
OL,12,Fthings."
OL,14,FIf the proposed legislation passes the
OL,15,FThird Reading it will progress onto
OL,16,Fthe Legislative Council for further
OL,17,Fdebate and scrutiny.
